
README for post processor.

To visualize the heatmaps corresponding to the .mar files created by the simulator
run main.m using matlab. This file has to be modified to adjust input files and
response variables. Everything is hardcoded

The main lines to change are:

pattern="..."

is a wildcard indicating the .mat files corresponding to a particular experiment (there is 1 .mat file
for each pixel).

It is possible to change other presentation features but for the main text it should not be necessary to change
anything else.


